select P.PROJID ,NAME ,PROJGROUPID ,TYPE ,STATUS ,CREATED ,PROJECTEDSTARTDATE ,STARTDATE ,PROJECTEDENDDATE ,ENDDATE ,PROJINVOICEPROJID ,CUSTACCOUNT ,PARENTID ,SORTINGID ,SORTINGID2_ ,SORTINGID3_ ,H1.PERSONNELNUMBER SALESMANAGER ,H2.PERSONNELNUMBER PROJECTMANAGER ,H3.PERSONNELNUMBER PROJECTCONTROLLER ,SQ2.PERCENT_ ,SubQ.PROJCLASS ,SubQ.CCENTER ,SubQ.CUSTGRP ,SubQ.DEPT ,SubQ.ITEMGRP ,LL.DESCRIPTION ,LPA.ADDRESS ,LPA.CITY ,LPA.STATE ,LPA.ZIPCODE ,LPA.COUNTY ,DATAAREAID ,WCI_WARRANTYSTARTDATE AS WARRANTY_START_DATE ,WCI_WARRANTYENDDATE AS WARRANTY_END_DATE ,WCICONTRACTDATE AS CONTRACT_DATE ,LPA.COUNTRYREGIONID AS COUNTRY ,P.ARPPORTID AS PORTFOLIO ,case when OB_Rev is null then 0 else OB_Rev end OB_Rev ,case when OB_Cost is null then 0 else OB_Cost end OB_Cost ,WCI_INVENTLOCATIONID InvLocCode from PROJTABLE P left outer join HCMWORKER H1 on P.WORKERRESPONSIBLESALES=H1.RECID left outer join HCMWORKER H2 on P.WORKERRESPONSIBLE=H2.RECID left outer join HCMWORKER H3 on P.WORKERRESPONSIBLEFINANCIAL=H3.RECID
left outer join (select C.PROJID, PERCENT_ from PSAPROJWORKCOMPLETE C inner join (select PROJID,MAX(TRANSDATE) TDATE from PSAPROJWORKCOMPLETE group by PROJID) SQ1 on C.PROJID=SQ1.PROJID and C.TRANSDATE=SQ1.TDATE) SQ2 on P.PROJID=SQ2.PROJID
left outer join (select Q.DAVS ,Q1.DV PROJCLASS ,Q2.DV CCENTER ,Q3.DV CUSTGRP ,Q4.DV DEPT ,Q5.DV ITEMGRP from (select I.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESET DAVS from DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE A inner join DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE V on A.RECID=V.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE inner join DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESETITEM I on V.RECID=I.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE group by I.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESET) Q
left outer join (select I.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESET DAVS ,A.NAME ,I.DISPLAYVALUE DV from DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE A inner join DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE V on A.RECID=V.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE inner join DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESETITEM I on V.RECID=I.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE where A.NAME='ProjectClassification') Q1 on Q.DAVS=Q1.DAVS
left outer join (select I.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESET DAVS ,A.NAME ,I.DISPLAYVALUE DV from DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE A inner join DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE V on A.RECID=V.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE inner join DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESETITEM I on V.RECID=I.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE where A.NAME='CostCenter') Q2 on Q.DAVS=Q2.DAVS
left outer join (select I.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESET DAVS ,A.NAME ,I.DISPLAYVALUE DV from DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE A inner join DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE V on A.RECID=V.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE inner join DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESETITEM I on V.RECID=I.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE where A.NAME='CustomerGroup') Q3 on Q.DAVS=Q3.DAVS
left outer join (select I.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESET DAVS ,A.NAME ,I.DISPLAYVALUE DV from DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE A inner join DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE V on A.RECID=V.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE inner join DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESETITEM I on V.RECID=I.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE where A.NAME='Division') Q4 on Q.DAVS=Q4.DAVS
left outer join (select I.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESET DAVS ,A.NAME ,I.DISPLAYVALUE DV from DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE A inner join DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE V on A.RECID=V.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTE inner join DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUESETITEM I on V.RECID=I.DIMENSIONATTRIBUTEVALUE where A.NAME='ItemGroup') Q5 on Q.DAVS=Q5.DAVS) SubQ on P.DEFAULTDIMENSION=SubQ.DAVS
left outer join LOGISTICSLOCATION LL on P.DELIVERYLOCATION=LL.RECID
left outer join LOGISTICSPOSTALADDRESS LPA on P.DELIVERYLOCATION=LPA.LOCATION and LPA.VALIDTO='2154-12-31 23:59:59.000'
left outer join ( select ROOTPROJID ProjNo ,sum(ORIGINALBUDGET) OB_Rev from PROJBUDGET b left outer join PROJBUDGETLINE l on b.RECID=l.PROJBUDGET where PROJBUDGETLINETYPE=0 group by ROOTPROJID )obr on p.PROJID=obr.ProjNo
left outer join ( select ROOTPROJID ProjNo ,sum(ORIGINALBUDGET) OB_Cost from PROJBUDGET b left outer join PROJBUDGETLINE l on b.RECID=l.PROJBUDGET where PROJBUDGETLINETYPE=1 group by ROOTPROJID )obc on p.PROJID=obc.ProjNo
